<title type="html"><![CDATA[combine prg and chr file?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3354&amp;p=26093#p26093"><![CDATA[
Use Total Commander (Windows Commander)<br /><br />Reneme files with added 001, 002, 003 (or more if hou have more files) as extension and click mouse on first file to combine into one file (xxx.out)<br /><br />example:<br /><br />nesdemo.hdr -&gt; nesdemo.001<br />nesdemo.prg -&gt; nesdemo.002<br />nesdemo.chr -&gt; nesdemo.003<br />and run first 001 file (click mouse on it) for make nesdemo.out (combined all three files) <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /><br /><br />Fast and easy  <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=411">sdm</a> — Wed Aug 01, 2007 11:07 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
