<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3354&amp;p=24017#p24017"><![CDATA[
uCON64 isn't very good at NES stuff. AFAIK to join a PRG and CHR file with uCON64, you'd need to make a fake Pasofami header file which is dumb. You'd be better off using the DOS tool COPY.<br /><br />copy /b file.prg + file.chr newfile.out<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=20">kyuusaku</a> — Sun May 06, 2007 5:40 pm</p><hr />
